        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>School Security Enhancement Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Elementary and Secondary Education Act of 1965 to allow local educational agencies to use specified portions of&nbsp;Student Support and Academic Enrichment grants for planning and designing school buildings and facilities, installing infrastructure, and implementing other measures to strengthen security on school premises. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
